data.value:
Bear Brand Fortified Reconstituted Milk Drink 180ml is a ready-to-drink milk beverage from Nestlé Philippines, designed to support children's growth and immune health. It combines the convenience of a shelf-stable drink with the nutritional benefits of essential vitamins and minerals.
Type of Milk: Reconstituted filled milk (from skimmed milk powder and milk fat)
Ideal For: Children aged 3 and above, and adults seeking a fortified milk drink
Ingredients: Water, recombined milk (from skimmed milk powder and milk fat), sucrose (sugar), stabilizers (such as carrageenan), and added vitamins and minerals including Vitamin C, Zinc Sulfate, Calcium Carbonate, Ferrous Sulfate (Iron), Vitamin A, Vitamin D3, and B-Vitamins (B1, B2, B6, B12, Niacin, Folic Acid) .
Where to buy: SM Supermarket Pasay, Puregold Quezon
______________________________________________________________________________
Nutrition Facts (per 180ml serving) Calories: 123 kcal
Total Fat: 6.7g
Saturated Fat: 3.3g
Carbohydrates: 11g
Sugars: 11g
Protein: 4g
Calcium: Approximately 231mg
Iron: Approximately 3.9mg
Vitamin C: Provides 100% of the Recommended Energy and Nutrient Intake (RENI) for children aged 4-6 years
